If the system is time dependent, the solenoidity is a necessary result of Faraday's equation, so

\begin{eqnarray}
\nabla \cdot \mathbf{E}&=& \frac{\rho_e}{\varepsilon_0} \label{maxwell_freespace1_simpli4}\\
